---
---
<header class="cover" id="top" style="background-image:url('/logo-bg.jpg'); background-size:cover; background-position:center">
  <svg class="cover__pattern" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#maskpat)" opacity="0.14"/></svg>
  <div class="wrap cover__inner">
    <span class="eyebrow cover__tag">Communauté · IA · Afrique francophone</span>

    <div class="cover__lockup reveal">
      <img src="/logo-white.jpg" alt="Y'TILIKAN" class="cover__logo" width="108" height="108" />
      <div class="cover__word">Y<span class="apos">'</span>TILIKAN</div>
    </div>

    <div class="cover__tagline reveal" data-delay="80"><em>« Ce n'est pas sorcier. »</em></div>

    <p class="cover__sub reveal" data-delay="160">
      La communauté de partage qui vulgarise et rend accessible la technologie —
      et surtout l'intelligence artificielle — pour la communauté africaine et
      sa diaspora.
    </p>

    <div class="cover__cta reveal" data-delay="240">
      <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@YTILIKAN" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn--gold">Voir les émissions</a>
      <a href="#contact" class="btn btn--ghost">Rejoindre la communauté</a>
    </div>

    <p class="cover__translate reveal" data-delay="320">y'tilikan · mooré → « ce n'est pas sorcier »</p>
  </div>
</header>

<style>
  .cover {
    background: var(--indigo);
    color: var(--ivoire);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    min-height: 92vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .cover__pattern { position: absolute; inset: 0; pointer-events: none; }
  .cover__inner { position: relative; z-index: 2; padding: 100px 0 80px; width: 100%; }
  .cover__tag { color: var(--ocre); }

  .cover__lockup {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 26px;
    margin: 26px 0 30px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .cover__logo { width: 108px; height: 108px; border-radius: 12px; object-fit: contain; flex: none; }
  .cover__word {
    font-family: var(--display);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 10vw, 6rem);
    letter-spacing: -.01em;
    line-height: .9;
  }
  .cover .apos { color: var(--ocre); }

  .cover__tagline {
    font-family: var(--display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 4.5vw, 2.8rem);
    letter-spacing: -.01em;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .cover__tagline em { font-style: normal; color: var(--ocre); }

  .cover__sub {
    max-width: 54ch;
    font-size: 1.14rem;
    color: #d9d2c4;
  }

  .cover__cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    margin: 38px 0 34px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    font-family: var(--display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: .95rem;
    padding: 13px 26px;
    border-radius: 40px;
    transition: transform .2s, background .2s, border-color .2s;
  }
  .btn--gold { background: var(--ocre); color: var(--encre); }
  .btn--gold:hover { background: var(--ocre-d); transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .btn--ghost { border: 1.5px solid #ffffff33; color: var(--ivoire); }
  .btn--ghost:hover { border-color: var(--ocre); color: var(--ocre); }

  .cover__translate {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: .8rem;
    letter-spacing: .05em;
    color: #b9c0d6;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--ocre);
    padding-left: 14px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .cover__mark { width: 76px; height: 76px; }
  }
</style>
